<section class="community-advice">
  <img class="section-badge" src="{{ "lp-community-section-badge-advice.png" | file_url }}" alt="community advice">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Need Advice? Ask The Community Everything.</h2>
    <p>Whenever you need advice, have questions, doubts, or want to see how other people deal with a situation, that’s the perfect time for you to post in the community!
    <br><br>
    The power of 100,000 diabetics in one place is enormous. Together we are the biggest knowledge center for diabetes on Earth. There is no better place in the world for you to get the answer to all your questions, big or small. So feel safe and comfortable posting and asking about anything at all!</p>
    <div class="posts desktop">
      <img class="quote-sign" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-quote-sign.png" | file_url }}" alt="community quote-sign">
      <img class="quote-sign" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-quote-sign.png" | file_url }}" alt="community quote-sign">
      <img class="posts" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-posts.png" | file_url }}" alt="community advice posts">
    </div>
    <div class="posts mobile swiper">
      <div class="swiper-wrapper">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-post-1.png" | file_url }}" alt="community advice posts">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-post-2.png" | file_url }}" alt="community advice posts">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-post-3.png" | file_url }}" alt="community advice posts">
        <img class="post swiper-slide" src="{{ "lp-community-advice-post-4.png" | file_url }}" alt="community advice posts">
      </div>
      <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
    </div>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/winningtype2diabetestogether/" target=”_blank”><button>Ask for Advice</button></a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .community-advice .quote-sign:nth-of-type(1) {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .community-advice .quote-sign:nth-of-type(2) {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
  }

  .community-advice .posts {
    position: relative;
  }

  .community-advice .posts.mobile {
    display: none;
  }

  .swiper-pagination-bullet-active {
    background: #475993;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 991px) {
    .community-advice .posts.mobile {
      display: block;
      overflow: visible;
    }

    .community-advice .posts.desktop {
      display: none;
    }

    .swiper-pagination {
      bottom: -30px !important;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  peoplePostsSlider = new Swiper('.community-advice .swiper', {
    slidesPerView: 1,
    spaceBetween: 20,
    watchSlidesVisibility: false,
    loop: false,
    slideToClickedSlide: true,
    pagination: {
        el: '.community-advice .swiper-pagination',
        clickable: 'true',
        type: 'bullets',
    },
    breakpoints: {
      640: {
        slidesPerView: 2,
      },
      991: {
        pagination: {}
      }
    }
  });
</script>